# Public Content Audit Allowlist
#
# Literal patterns (one per line). Lines matching any pattern are exempt
# from ALL block and warn checks. Lines starting with # are comments.
# Case-insensitive matching.

# --- Glasswing proper names (Anthropic's program) ---
Project Glasswing
Glasswing-Anthropic
Glasswing-class
Glasswing/Mythos

# --- NVIDIA technology ---
Optimus PRIME
PRIME render-offload

# --- Stanford research ---
openjarvis

# --- Owner-allowed names in maintainer/attribution contexts ---
Christopher Cork
Chris Cork
InterGenJLU
Ethan Bambock

# --- PGP UID format ---
chris@intergenstudios.com

# --- Legitimate all-caps uses in public docs ---
# CONTRIBUTING.md section header for Prime Directive
PRIME DIRECTIVE
# References to this audit script itself
check-public-content

